Description: Download mail from Hotmail accounts
DescDetail: <<
GotMail is a Perl script which downloads mail messages from a HotMail
account and either saves them to disk or forwards them to another
email address. It can either be used to transfer all the mail out of
an account for backups, or on a regular basis to use a HotMail address
as a forwarding account.
<<
